# F1 Telemetry & AI Race Engineer Dashboard - Backend

Environment configuration for the FastAPI backend server.
Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your actual values.

## Database Configuration
DB_USER=postgres
DB_PASSWORD=your_postgres_password
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=5432
DB_NAME=f1_telemetry

## API Configuration
API_HOST=0.0.0.0
API_PORT=8000
DEBUG=False

## FastF1 Configuration
FASTF1_CACHE_DIR=./cache
FASTF1_REQUESTS_TIMEOUT=30

## LLM API Keys
# OpenAI Configuration
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here
OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4

# Google Gemini Configuration
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here
GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-pro

# Active LLM Provider (options: openai, gemini)
ACTIVE_LLM_PROVIDER=openai

## Frontend URL (for CORS)
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000

## Logging
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
